Accessible, ImageObserver, MenuContainer, RootPaneContainer, Serializable, WindowConstants
public class Identify
extends JDialog

This class displays multiple features with a list and table UI. The list contains the values of a "representative" field of the features and the table displays all the (field, value) pairs of the currently selected feature on the list. This class can be used as a visual ui for the identify tool and the editNotes tool.
